      "author": "vilstr17",
      "description": "## 1.1.0\n\nFirst release under the **Chronote** name (renamed from Cortex).\n\n### What's new\n- **Rename:** plugin id, UI, prompts, and settings migrated Cortex → Chronote.\n- **Multi-provider AI agent:** Gemini, OpenAI-compatible, Anthropic, and local providers (Ollama, LM Studio).\n- **Google Calendar** scheduling + spaced-repetition reviews and tests.\n- **Flashcards:** per-save location picker + study view.\n- **Infra:** migrated to Node16 ESM; CI gates (typecheck, lint, coverage); security hardening; privacy policy.\n\n### Fixes\n- Restored `console.warn`/`console.error` logging in the tool registry and `list_tests`.\n- Restored coverage thresholds (added `settingsMigration` fs-reader tests; re-baselined `geminiService` functions floor).\n- Lint: removed an empty `onClose` override; documented an intentional empty `catch`.",
